<div id="review_1323325318" class="review nosyndicate" itemprop="reviews" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Review">
  <link itemprop="url" href="https://www.goodreads.com/review/show/1323325318" />
    <a title="Janelle" class="left imgcol" href="/user/show/6097225-janelle"><img alt="Janelle" src="https://images.gr-assets.com/users/1493241562p2/6097225.jpg" /></a>

  <div class="left bodycol">
    <div class="reviewHeader uitext stacked">
        <a class="reviewDate createdAt right" href="/review/show/1323325318?book_show_action=true">Jul 02, 2015</a>

      <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Person">
        <a title="Janelle" class="user" itemprop="url" name="Janelle" href="/user/show/6097225-janelle">Janelle</a>
      </span>

        rated it
        <span class=" staticStars notranslate" title="it was amazing"><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10">it was amazing</span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span></span>



        

          <div class="uitext greyText bookshelves">
            Shelves:
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/6097225-janelle?shelf=5-stars">5-stars</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/6097225-janelle?shelf=kids-books">kids-books</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/6097225-janelle?shelf=historical">historical</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/6097225-janelle?shelf=audiobooks-read">audiobooks-read</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/6097225-janelle?shelf=classics">classics</a>
          </div>
    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer1323325318" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer5981765937998735069">Delightful shenanigans with four children who are left home alone suspiciously often. I had considered only giving it four stars, due to frequent references to savages and naive notions about burglars. Not to mention comments that it&apos;s unmanly for boys to cry. But I just can&apos;t help myself. It&apos;s just too wonderful for four stars. Many thanks go to the Librivox narrator, Helen Taylor, for her beautiful reading. </span>
  <span id="freeText5981765937998735069" style="display:none">Delightful shenanigans with four children who are left home alone suspiciously often. I had considered only giving it four stars, due to frequent references to savages and naive notions about burglars. Not to mention comments that it's unmanly for boys to cry. But I just can't help myself. It's just too wonderful for four stars. Many thanks go to the Librivox narrator, Helen Taylor, for her beautiful reading. </span>
  <a data-text-id="5981765937998735069" href="#" onclick="swapContent($(this));; return false;">...more</a>

          </span>
        </div>


